- check out Emacs Code Browser: http://ecb.sourceforge.net


- Switch to spacemacs-base and add the following packages:
  - auto-highlight-symbol
  - buffer-move
  - evil-exchange? - exchange 2 text objects
  - evil-mc - MULTIPLE CURSORS!!!!
  - evil-matchit
  - expand-region
  - flx-ido
  - golden-ratio
  - helm-ag
  - helm-swoop - aquele search altamente!
  - highlight-parentheses
  - hungry-delete - delete whole blocks of whitespace
  - info+ - improves readability of emacs documentation
  - iedit - edit multiple ocurrences of symbol simultaneously
  - indent-guid
  - rainbow-delimiters
  - smartparens - only if you learn how to work with it...
  - smooth-scrolling
  - spaceline
  - volatile-highlights
